markets plunge in the last week showed that the bubble 
phenomenon had finally burst 
stock purchasing by investors on borrowed cash at low interest 
rates had inflated share values he said 
but a sharp rise in interest rates last year spelled an end to 
obtaining easy cash the bank of japan the nations central bank 
raised the key discount rate three times last year and it now 
stands at 425 percent 
