plan on the federal role the state role and the local role 
timothy dyer the new president of the national association of 
secondary school principals said americas governors receive an 
aplus for rhetoric but fail economics their goals are lofty 
patriotic noble and certainly what we all would like however 
without resources they are merely wishes 
