wanted a political agreement reached with the lebanese forces 
before the committee continues with its plan for reopening roads 
stabilizing the ceasefire without a political agreement would 
undercut aouns declared objective that the lebanese forces should 
disband and become a political organization geagea refuses to 
break up his military force 
geageas fighters control twothirds of the christian enclave 
including its three main ports and two isolated pockets on the 
northwestern edge of beirut 
