government intervenes to halt the christian feuding 
hrawi elected nov 24 is recognized by geagea but rejected by 
aoun who considers himself the sole legitimate authority in 
lebanon the syrians have 40000 troops in lebanon under a 1976 
arab league peacekeeping mandate aoun considers them an occupation 
army 
