burstyn attorney for former panamanian army lt col luis del cid 
at some point the lieutenant colonel may be confronted with 
an option he cant refuse 
burstyn refused to reveal details except to say the proposed 
sentence would be far less than the 40 years del cid was offered 
when taken into custody on drugtrafficking charges and he added 
that the deal had not yet been signed 
