president daniel ortega said monday 
his sandinistas will honor the voters wishes and surrender power 
to a 6monthold opposition alliance that won an upset victory 
after a decade of oneparty rule 
we leave victorious because the sandinistas have sacrificed 
spilled blood and sweat not to cling to government posts but to 
