ive always wanted to go into my own business and this just 
sort of fell into my lap she says whats more is that all of 
my clients treat me like im some kind of a hero 
one of her clients with a newborn baby said her 4yearold was 
watching her change the baby with a disposable diaper and had a 
quizzical look on her face 
what is it asked the mother 
why dont they invent a diaper you could just wash and use 
over and over asked the child 
