president bush 
there have been changes in his life with success but hes still 
the same softspoken randy travis 
it hasnt changed me as a person he said in an interview 
its changed my lifestyle i live out of a suitcase on the road 
but i still enjoy doing the same things i always have i still 
enjoy the same people and the same music 
