week which he said were at 783000 and 901000 respectively 
a few years after taking over the business forbes decided to 
diversify into other areas he purchased ranch land in colorado and 
land by lakes in missouri parts of which have been made available 
for sale 
the company acquired laucala one of the fiji islands in the 
south pacific where executives can go on retreats in keeping with 
his wishes forbes body will be cremated and the ashes buried on 
the island 
forbes invited dozens of bigwigs to his palace in tangier 
morocco last year for his 70th birthday party visitors to the 
forbes building in new york can see a collection of jeweled 
farberge eggs that were made in czarist russia 
forbes owns the old battersea house on the river thames in 
london which he used only last week for an international bridge 
tournament featuring some top corporate chiefs he was stricken 
only hours after his return from london early saturday 
his fortune has been estimated at between 400 million and 12 
billion 
all of these holdings helped forbes cultivate contacts with 
corporate executives which he hoped made them more disposed to buy 
advertising with his magazine indeed he initially suggested he 
might be able to write off the 2 million cost of his moroccan 
birthday bash as a business expense 
forbes also expanded his publishing holdings the forbes company 
owns american heritage magazine a monthly that specializes in 
stories about important historical events only a week ago forbes 
